Nike LeBron 18 Low atmos Cherry Blossom
results.story: Designed in partnership with the influential Tokyo-based retailer, the atmos x Nike LeBron 18 Low ‘Cherry Blossom’ showcases a spring-ready design, highlighted by a Swoosh formed with pink embroidered florals. The pastel hue is repeated on the sneaker’s molded eyelets and TPU heel counter, as well as a multicolor geometric print that enlivens the textile upper. The low-top sits on a cushy React foam midsole with a large-volume Max Air unit nestled under the heel.

results.name: Nike SB Dunk High Hawaii
results.story: The Nike Dunk High SB ‘Maui Wowie’ makes use of a floral-print textile upper, accented with undyed hemp on the Swoosh and tongue. The outer layer on the toe box and quarter panels are designed to tear away, revealing a different floral print rendered in fiery red and orange hues. The sneaker’s forefoot and heel overlays, meanwhile, feature shaggy green suede beneath the tear-away surface layer. The multi-color arrangement up top is countered by a crisp white midsole, supported underfoot by a cream-colored rubber outsole.

Nike Cosmic Unity Apricot Agate
results.story: Inspired by the natural world, the Nike Cosmic Unity ‘Pomegranate’ highlights pastel hues on a performance basketball shoe built with 25% recycled materials by weight. Peach-colored textile is utilized throughout the upper, equipped with a plush tongue decorated with a pomegranate graphic. A scientific infographic on the sockliner reveals that the fruit’s rind was used to create some of the shoe’s coloring. The sneaker is mounted on a podular foam midsole that’s supplemented by a full-length Air Zoom Strobel.

Nike Air Huarache Scream Green (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Huarache ‘Scream Green’ brings back an OG colorway of Tinker Hatfield’s revolutionary running shoe in honor of its 30th anniversary. The Swoosh-free upper combines bootie-style neoprene construction in blue and fluorescent green. A midfoot overlay in white tumbled leather delivers structural support and durability, along with an exoskeletal heel cage with embossed Nike branding on the back strap. The lightweight build is mounted on a Phylon midsole with encapsulated Nike Air in the heel for enhanced cushioning with each stride.

Nike Dunk Low Green Glow (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Green Glow’ showcases traditional color blocking on a customary all-leather build. A crisp white base is contrasted by a vibrant shade of green on the sneaker’s eyestay, Swoosh, and forefoot and heel overlays. The verdant hue is repeated on the woven tongue tag and heel tab, both marked with standard Nike branding. The low-top rides on a two-tone rubber cupsole, equipped with a grippy outsole originally designed for pivoting on the hardwood.

results.name: Nike Air Griffey Max 1 Varsity Royal (PS) (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Griffey Max 1 PS ‘Varsity Royal’ revives Ken Griffey Jr.’s debut signature shoe in little kids sizing. Originally released in 1996, the retro trainer features a bright blue nubuck upper with contrasting white leather paneling. Volt-colored Swooshes adorn the heel and adjustable ankle strap, the latter also featuring Junior’s jersey number with the Seattle Mariners. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a foam midsole fitted with a visible Max Air unit under the heel.

results.name: Nike Air Foamposite One All-Star 2021
results.story: Launching as part of the brand’s ‘All Star 2021’ collection, the Nike Air Foamposite One ‘Glow’ features a sleek black finish throughout the distinctive synthetic shell upper, formed by pouring liquid polyurethane into a custom mold. The monochromatic color scheme is disrupted by the sneaker’s branding elements, including a white mini-Swoosh on the lateral forefoot and an NBA All-Star emblem on the back heel. The sneaker rides on a semi-translucent glow-in-the-dark rubber outsole.

results.name: Nike Air Griffey Max 1 Varsity Royal (TD) (2021)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air Griffey Max 1 TD ‘Varsity Royal’ brings back a scaled-down version of Ken Griffey Jr.’s signature shoe on the occasion of its 25th anniversary. Inspired by the Seattle Mariners’ vintage ‘80s uniforms, the trainer features a nubuck and leather upper in blue and white. The Kid’s jersey number adorns the adjustable ankle strap, which works in tandem with elastic no-tie laces for a secure fit. The midsole packs a Volt-colored Air sole unit under the heel for lightweight cushioning.

results.name: Nike Dunk Low Michigan (GS)
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Dunk Low GS ‘Michigan’ brings back one of the original colorways of the brand’s iconic ‘Be True to Your School’ series from 1985, reimagined as a low-top and offered in big kid sizing. Paying homage to the Wolverines of Ann Arbor, the low-profile silhouette carries an all-leather upper in Midnight Navy and Varsity Maize hues. Retro details include a perforated toe box and a lightly padded nylon tongue topped with a woven Nike tag.

results.name: Nike Air Griffey Max 1 Varsity Royal (GS) (2021)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Nike Air Griffey Max 1 GS ‘Varsity Royal’ brings back Ken Griffey Jr.’s signature shoe in big kids sizing. The retro color scheme is inspired by the Seattle Mariners and features a vibrant blue nubuck upper with contrasting white synthetic leather paneling. Volt-colored accents make their way to Nike Swoosh branding on the heel and adjustable ankle strap, the latter further accented with the Kid’s jersey number with the Mariners. Additional pops of Volt appear on the midsole, enhanced with Max Air units under the heel and forefoot.

results.name: Nike Air Huarache Escape (2021)
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Nike Air Huarache ‘Escape’ brings back a 2003 colorway that originally released as part of an expansive outdoor-inspired pack. Complementary earth tones are executed on the upper, featuring a tan nubuck toe and stretchy bootie construction in grey and dark green hues. A brown nubuck midfoot cage connects to a heel strap that replaces a traditional heel counter. The minimalist build is supported by a plush Phylon midsole with full-length Nike Air cushioning.

results.name: Dunk Low PS 'Michigan' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Dunk Low PS ‘Michigan’ brings back an OG colorway in little kids sizing. Rendered in low-top form, the retro hoops shoe features a simple two-tone design that pays homage to the Michigan Wolverines — one of the universities included in 1985’s classic ‘Be True to Your School’ pack. An all-leather upper in Varsity Maize and Midnight Navy sits atop a contrasting white midsole. Standard Nike branding decorates the woven tongue tag and heel tab.

Air More Uptempo TD 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air More Uptempo TD ‘White Varsity Red’ delivers a scaled-down version of an early 2000s colorway alternately known as the ‘Renowned Rhythm.’ Like the original, the leather upper is dominated by oversized ‘Air’ lettering outlined in red. Pull tabs at the tongue and heel combine with no-tie elastic laces for easy on and off. The foam midsole houses an encapsulated Air pod under the heel that provides lightweight cushioning for little feet.

results.name: Mercurial Superfly 8 Academy MG GS 'Metallic Silver Volt'
Air More Uptempo PS 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 reissue of the Nike Air More Uptempo PS ‘White Varsity Red’ revives a 2005 release in little kids sizing. The elemental two-tone colorway, alternately known as the ‘Renowned Rhythm,’ displays prominent ‘Air’ branding across the white leather upper, with each oversized letter outlined in red. A lightweight foam midsole is enhanced with visible Nike Air cushioning in the heel. Underfoot, the rubber outsole features a herringbone traction pattern for reliable grip.

results.name: Nike Air Griffey Max 1 Jackie Robinson
results.story: The Nike Air Griffey Max 1 ‘Jackie Robinson’ pays tribute to the iconic athlete who broke Major League Baseball’s color barrier in 1947. Ken Griffey Jr.’s debut signature shoe is clad in a black leather upper with contrasting white accents. Each adjustable ankle strap is marked with Robinson’s jersey number and inscribed with one of his inspirational quotes. Embossed on the left strap is text that reads ‘There’s not an American in this country free until every one of us is free.’ On the right, ‘A life is not important except in the impact it has on other lives.’

results.name: Air More Uptempo GS 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air More Uptempo GS ‘White Varsity Red’ brings back a simplistic 2005 colorway in big kids sizing. Alternately dubbed the ‘Renowned Rhythm,’ the vintage hoops shoe features a perforated white leather upper with oversized ‘Air’ lettering outlined in red. Retro details include dual pull loops, a jewel Swoosh at the heel and a speed lacing system augmented by elastic straps. The mid-top sits on a full-length Phylon midsole with a visible Air sole unit under the heel.

results.name: Mercurial Superfly 8 Academy MG 'Metallic Silver Volt'
Air More Uptempo 'White Varsity Red' 2021
results.story: The 2021 edition of the Nike Air More Uptempo ‘White Varsity Red’ brings back a simple two-tone colorway also known as the ‘Renowned Rhythm,’ a reference to the dynamic playing style of Chicago Bulls forward Scottie Pippen. Originally released in the mid-2000s and previously reissued in 2018, the mid-top sports a pristine white leather upper, accented with oversized ‘AIR’ lettering outlined in red. A matching crimson jewel Swoosh adorns the back heel. Three distinct Nike Air units are housed in a lightweight Phylon midsole, supported underfoot by a herringbone rubber outsole.
